Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE as the exclusive sales agent, is pleased to present 118-120, 122 Main Street, Blacktown. Two (2) freestanding high yielding freehold buildings with significant development upside (STCA) in the heart of Blacktown’s thriving retail strip. 

Offered with a generous land holding of 601sqm* and rear lane access on a commanding main road, the property is opportunely positioned within walking distance to Blacktown Train Station and Westpoint Shopping Centre. Additionally, six (6) existing tenancies are available to the site presenting multiple reliable income streams, generating  approximately $210,635 gross annual income.  


118-120, 122 Main Street, Blacktown benefits from the following key attributes:

•Significantly recognised land holding of 601sqm*
•Six (6) existing tenancies generating approximately $210,635 gross annual income
•Prominent corner location offering premium exposure
•Extensive glass facades with maximum exposure & street appeal
•Partially leased with extensive tenant fit-out
•Value add return on investment
•Considerate development potential (STCA)
•B4 mixed use zoning, ideal for shop top housing, childcare facilities, hotel accommodation and medical centres 
•Height of building limit of 50 metres 
•Located in Blacktown’s thriving retail strip surrounded by boutique retail stores, shopping centers, parks, schools and transport.  
•High pedestrian thoroughfare providing pronounced foot and vehicle traffic to the property. 
•Within walking distance to Blacktown Train Station

118-120, 122 Main Street, Blacktown will be offered for Auction on Friday 16 July 2021, at 3:00pm.

Venue: Online - Registration Link: https://auctionslive.com/app/bidder-registration/40kv

For more information or to request access to the due diligence room, please contact the exclusive selling agents.

*Approx.

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: HIGH YIELDING FREEHOLD BUILDINGS WITH DEVELOPMENT UPSIDE! (STCA)

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE is pleased to offer this residential development site in the western Sydney suburb of Blacktown, being 13 kilometres from Parramatta CBD.

The site is located nearby to Blacktown Train Station, shopping facilities, well regarded schools, parks and employment centres.

The site has Development Approval for the construction of a 6 level residential apartment building over two levels of basement carparking.

Key Features:
•	Development Approval
•	67 Apartments 
•	400 metres to Blacktown Train Station*
•	Site Area of 2,500sqm*
•	Gross Floor Area (GFA) of 5,675sqm*
* Approx.

This premier residential development opportunity is for sale via an Expression of Interest campaign.

All Expressions of Interest are to be submitted in writing to CBRE by Thursday 28th June 2018 at 5pm (AEST).

For more information please contact the exclusive agents: 

         Ben Wicks                   0422 206 015
         Alex Mirzaian             0400 523 523

The property is located on the corner of Richmond Road & Davis Road in Blacktown. The subject site is a short distance from Blacktown showground and Ashlar Golf Course.

The site is 1,502 sqm approximately over two titles and irregular in shape.

The property is zoned Residential 2(a) under Blacktown City Council.

*Prime exposure on corner site, 3 street frontages

*Site area 1,441 sqm*

*Excellent future development opportunity (STCA)

*Close proximity to Blacktown CBD and major transport routes
